<ul>
  <li>80/20 rule -
    <ul>
      <li>80 percent of the people use 20 percent of the features. So you convince yourself that you only need to implement 20 percent of the features, and you can still sell 80 percent as many copies. Unfortunately, it‚Äôs never the same 20 percent. Everybody uses a different set of features</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
